Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Transformers Prime:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.60,0:00:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The planetary alignment,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.27,0:00:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to which the propehcy refers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.13,0:00:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is nearly upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.25,0:00:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The flaming mountain in my visions...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.64,0:00:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A place from whence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am to harvest Dark Energon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.94,0:00:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need him over here, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.03,0:00:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megatron, today you answer for your crimes against Cybertron and humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.83,0:00:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pulse rate is stabilizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.98,0:00:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the blood of Unicron I've been seeking
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is not out there, but rather, right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hahaha...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.77,0:01:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the blood of Unicron erupting from beneath the Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A question, Optimus,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.64,0:01:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you shall take to your grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.47,0:01:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly! We must pull him trough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.54,0:01:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bulk, now, now, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.77,0:02:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is merely the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.09,0:02:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I now possess enough Dark Energon to reanimate Unicron himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hahaha... yes! Hahaha...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Easy, Optimus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}From the looks of things, you've been exposed to a mass of amount of Dark Energon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.61,0:03:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's lucky to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megatron found more of the dark stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Volcano full.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The question is, how?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}No, the question is, what,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.87,0:03:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as in what in the world is the blood of Unicron doing here on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 'Cons killed a Unicorn?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}White horse with a horn on its head...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}prances around all sparkly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.03,0:03:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Unicron, an ancient evil,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}whose fossilized blood comprises the matter which we call Dark Energon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:03:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... as legend would have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying, this Unicron is some kind of bogeyman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bogeyman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make believe creepy guy who hides in your closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Nurse Darby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unicron is very real... was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, while I do believe he once exited,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't subscribe to the theory that his...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,primordial life force is the substance which... harmed Raf.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard it enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack, please, help me get Raf into the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, I thought he was doing better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raf needs to be examined by really doctors,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Raf's family needs to know what's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His real family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, Raf's family can't protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like they can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,June, it deeply grieves me that I have failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I will do everything in my power to ensure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that no harm comes to our human friends or any human ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Optimus, they are children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They do not belong in your world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.81,0:05:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should be worrying about grades, prom dates, pimples...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not their own survival!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, Dark Energon is pouring out of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This could be about everyone's survival,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.18,0:05:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not just ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all three of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.66,0:05:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they will not be coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all we've been through together, "see ya"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about our freedom to choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That may fly on their planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but not here on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really expect me to ride in a non-transforming vehicle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miko, I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither are you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I am yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.33,0:06:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ratchet, activate the GroundBridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prime, do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you, Agent Fowler.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Been watching the news?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother nature's got a twitch in her breaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know about the volcano.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the quakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:07:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven major temblors of the exact the same magnitude at the exact same time as the volcanic eruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All over the globe on different plutonic plates, in theory unrelated, if they hadn't happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the exact same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.46,0:07:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check it out, more good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freak storms unlike any the region has seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tsunamis threaten the Canadian coast,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while lightning storms pummel the Gobi Desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.34,0:07:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, electro-magnetic anomalies plague urban power grids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These abnormal global phenomena are leaving most to wonder: why now, and what next?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me your 'Cons've built a weather machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One that powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Highly unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not believe the appearance of Dark Energon at this point in time to be coincidental.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One 100, two 100...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You OK back there, Raf?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting until the thunder...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:07:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, looks like a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My garden will love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raf, are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bee wants us to climb into his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.11,0:10:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says "You are welcome."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse of your very life blood rising from the depth to become one with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:10:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we are glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be. Jack...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.91,0:11:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're grounded till you're 30... 25.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,World leaders are classifying these bizarre weather patterns as a global emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Global?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And scientists believe the phenomena to be somehow
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,related to the current planetary alignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you learned, Prime?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you'd better not blow smoke up my ass...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Darby, What a nice surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Agent Fowler.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have learned this: as with the so called magma from the volcano,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these earthquakes originated far below the Earth's crust...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the very center of the Earth's core in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quakes don't start there, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:12:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiny tremors rising and falling in a consistent pattern, almost like...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.73,0:12:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by the All Spark...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I convert these data points to audio files...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.39,0:12:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Soundwave. Turn it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can still hear it pounding in my brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cybertronian heartbeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A heart pumps blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.92,0:12:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing inside the Earth to pump except...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood of Unicron.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean something's living down there,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,inside our planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fear that the Earth's very core is not comprised of magma
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.83,0:13:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as your science has suggested, but of Dark Energon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.87,0:13:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if we're hearing a spark,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then Unicron is the rising darkness that the prophecy foretold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how do we stop this thing from rising?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I'm afraid was not foretold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can something be in our Earth core and be alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a thing is not unprecedented.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.71,0:13:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before the beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was Primus. And there was Unicron.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, the incarnation of creation,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:14:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the other... of destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For eons, Primus and Unicron battled,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the balance of power shifting between them more times than could be counted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only by creating the Thirteen--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the original Primes preceded me--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.78,0:14:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was Primus finally able to defeat Unicron and cast him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Primus became one with the very core of our planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.70,0:14:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,creating life through the Well of All Sparks,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.30,0:14:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while Unicron was never to be heard from again... until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.83,0:14:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we can find the hole this kuggo Con left when he dug himself all the way down there,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.43,0:14:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and fill it full of explosives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Fowler,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not believe that Earth became Unicron's home,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but rather that with time and gravitational force,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.73,0:15:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,debris collected around this slumbering titan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forming your Earth itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's only awakening now, due to the magnetic pull created by the planetary alignment?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.37,0:15:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok, what happens now when Unicron wakes up from his billion-year nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, does he stretch and ka-pow... Earth pup to dust?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My guess is that Unicron has transcended physical form as we know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonetheless, we must find a way to ensure that this "force of nature" never fully awakens.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.81,0:15:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fate of your planet depends upon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Megatron, our cargo hold is nearly filled with the dark substance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I recommend a retreat,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the troops are growing weak from its effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet I grow stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Airachnid, you're in command until my return.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your return from where, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From my audience with Unicron.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel your presents,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,share your very spark.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.65,0:16:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I call on you as my Lord and Master, almighty Unicron.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would speak to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.01,0:16:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your servant most humble,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megatron, leader of the Decepticons,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and your very Herald,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the one who wielded the Dark Energon which binds us,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to awaken you once again. The prophecy has been fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is only the beginning of what we shall accomplish, together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For you shall rule this planet and those who walk upon it through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pride for fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you think yourself capable of summoning my life force?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I rise because I have deemed my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, I did not mean to overstep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence, worm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.79,0:17:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no need of your lowly assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, my Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I exist only to serve you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this I sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The taint of Primus? Here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is Optimus,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the last of the Primes, our sworn enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You profess loyalty to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yet allow a disciple of Primus to live?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will destroy him for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His screams will be heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.15,0:18:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I grow weary of your prattle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely if you had the power to destroy this Prime,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you would have done so already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.81,0:18:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will deal with him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ratchet, this epicenter is consistent with the findings of the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its terrain is rich in ore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what does that tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It follows that the natural medals in your Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would be extensions of Unicron-- his limbs if you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, he did have his morning stretch,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which is why these quakes happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Optimus, I'm detecting a swell of Unicron's spark activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.22,0:18:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest assured, Ratchet,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:18:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will proceed with vigilance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know me, follower of Primus?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unicron, the Chaos Bringer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.58,0:19:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now know me as Unicron, your destroyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I humbly request your ear, Lord Unicron.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what would a Prime be so compelled to say to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.53,0:19:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I make this appeal not for myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for this planet which you constitute, and the beings who inhabit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.37,0:20:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Human kind relies upon you, for life, sustenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your resurrection will only result in the destruction of a spices
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which evolved from the seeds of your very greatness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this humankind of whom you speak,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you consider them my progeny?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Parasites! They, too, shall know my wrathful hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once I am finished with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The line of Primus has grown weak in my absence, and thus you shall fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That outcome is inevitable,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but not on this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, disciple of Primes, on this very day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.66,0:21:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Unicron may be one, but we all are Unicron.
